2014.12.18. version 1.0.0, jszigeti
-----------------------------------

Initial version containing:
* Base class structure (CsvCell, CsvRow, CsvPipe) with I/O functions.
* Column indentification functions (ColTypes).
* Selection classes and functions (RowFilter).
* Command-line tools: csvpipe, csvproj, csvfilter.
* Logger classes and macros.
* Command line option parser parent and derived classes.
Installation tool:
* autoconf/automake sources and generated scripts & files.
* libtool generates static / dynamic lib.
